SUMMARY:Strength Made Simple
DESCRIPTION:Are you… Feeling overwhelmed in the gym? Are you a fitness beginner? Plateaued in your training? Seeking confidence in your program?\nThis is for you!!! This workshop includes foundational education on exercise form\, proper warm up\, and cool down\, a nutritional blueprint and a training program to take home. Be prepared to lift\, move and sweat! Let’s make strength simple.
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/strength-made-simple/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Intro-to-lifting-2025-5.webp
