DESCRIPTION:🎯 NATIONAL LASER TAG DAY BLOWOUT 🎯\nCelebrate National Laser Tag Day with us on Saturday\, March 28!\nFor ONE DAY ONLY\, enjoy UNLIMITED Laser Tag for just $10 per person.\nBring your friends. Bring your family. Battle it out all day long.\n💥 $10 per person\n💥 Unlimited laser tag sessions\n💥 Saturday\, March 28\n💥 All ages welcome\nMark yourself as “Going” and invite your squad!\nLet’s pack the arena
